r />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"38751d316c0bfc98724c70d9cd82868d09e81c94","tid":2272213,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump - AMERICA FIRST<br />\n<br />\nThere will not be another wise man who love US the most.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec37954880658d0eb939f960796adce492f6bc7b","tid":2272213,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"美國TOP 100個有錢佬、科學家，求其搵一個都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}